:

1. *Doneo* je knjigu svojoj sestri. (He brought the book to his sister.)
2. Ona mu je *donela* novu majicu. (She brought him a new shirt.)
3. Njegov otac mu je *doneo* novi džepni sat. (His father brought him a new pocket watch.)
4. *Doneše* su svi potrebne stvari za putovanje. (They brought all the necessary items for the trip.)
5. Njegov prijatelj mu je *doneo* dar za rođendan. (His friend brought him a gift for his birthday.)